            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> Scan the whole live window (self._head .. self._tail - 1) for the packed metatable rather than just the first slot, so sanitization triggers whenever any element is a packed multivalue.\r\n\r\nUse the vendored benchmark script to compare results and make sure this doesn’t regress anything substantially.\r\n\r\nA lot of the code in vim.iter is the way that it is to make it fast.",
